{
  "texts": [
    "This loop continues until the instruction is clear, culminating in a detailed task plan executed by the robot.",
    "a) LLM generates the task plan focusing on: 1) Interact with Appliance: •Step 1: Analyze Instruction: -LLM detects ambiguity: Missing parameters (e.g., which room, what objects to clean, cleaning method).",
    "-Generated Prompt: \"Which room should I clean, and what objects need attention?\"",
    "• Step 2: User Response: -User replies: \"Clean the living room, and pick up the toys on the floor.\"",
    "• Step 3: Clarify Spatial and Handling Details: -LLM generates another prompt: \"Where should I place the toys after picking them up?\""
  ]
}